avg_ChangeDuration.query: q = load "${App.Datasets.LeadHistory_tp.FullyQualifiedName}";q = filter q by {{column(changeFieldID.selection, ["Lead_Name"]).asEquality("Lead_Name")}};q = group q by '{{column(filter_field.selection, ["LeadHistory"]).asObject()}}CurrentValue'; q = foreach q generate '{{column(filter_field.selection, ["LeadHistory"]).asObject()}}CurrentValue' as '{{column(filter_field.selection, ["LeadHistory"]).asObject()}}CurrentValue', avg('{{column(filter_field.selection, ["LeadHistory"]).asObject()}}DurationInHours') as 'avg_DurationInHours'; q = order q by 'avg_DurationInHours' desc;

Lead_IsConverted_1.label: Lead_IsConverted_1
Lead_IsConverted_1.query: a = load "${App.Datasets.LeadHistory_tp.FullyQualifiedName}";b = filter a by 'Lead_IsConverted' == "false";c = group a by 'StatusCurrentValue' full, b by 'StatusCurrentValue';c = foreach c generate coalesce(a['StatusCurrentValue'], b['StatusCurrentValue']) as 'Lead_Status', avg(a['StatusDurationInHours']) as 'Historical Average', avg(b['StatusDurationInHours']) as 'Open Leads Average';

table_details.label: table_details
table_details.query: q = load "${App.Datasets.LeadHistory_tp.FullyQualifiedName}"; q = foreach q generate 'Lead_Name','Lead_IsConverted','OwnerCurrentValue','Lead_Status','Lead_Account_Name','Lead_Contact_Name','Lead_Opportunity_Name','OwnerDurationInHours','StatusDurationInHours','CreatedDate';
